                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was called, and saw Robinson running with something in his bat - he jumped over a ditch, and I after him; he threw the shirts down; I tookthem up, and secured him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>ROBINSON'S Defence. I found the bundle by the bricks, and took it up.</p>
